values: 敌人；对手；仇敌；大敌；反对者；敌对势力

word_mean_info__list.difference: 最常用词，通常指在争论、辩论、竞选或竞赛以及其它各种矛盾冲突中站在对立面的“对手”或“敌手”。
指与某人目标一致而想赶上或超过他的人，匹敌者。
语气较强，多用于书面文字和诗歌中。指不仅敌对，而且很危险，怀有很深的敌意。
指为同一目标或目的竞争者，一般无感情色彩。

bilingual.source: Others think it was built to celebrate a victory over an enemy.
bilingual.target: 其他人认为它是为了庆祝战胜敌人而建造的。
我们必须面对我们的敌人。
他对敌人表现出了仁慈。

bilingual.target: 他们联合起来抵御敌人。

list.abstract: Enemy（英 [ˈenəmi]，美 [ˈenəmi]），英语单词，作名词为敌人；仇敌；反对者。例句：Eliminating the enemy one by one.（一个接一个地消灭敌人。） Enemy的近义词有foe、hostes、hostile，反义词有friend。

After we spoke I had a dream that I broke
The teeth from a mouth of a snake
That I choked on the teeth
They were mine all along
I picked up the pieces when I woke up
Put them in a boat made of things that I don't want to see
I blew on the sail
Watched it drift out to sea
The further it drifted the closer it came to me
I can't explain
So I took it apart built a billion boxes
There was only one key
You might think I'm your enemy
But that don't make you mine
And all I have now is empathy
I wish that you'd stop trying
Oh, please stop lying
Stop la la la la la la la
La la la la la...
I put hatred in a box then I locked it
The strongest one I made
I buried it all, grew a tree without thorns
And sat beneath the shade
You might think I'm your enemy
But that don't make you mine
And all I have now is empathy
I wish that you'd stop trying
Oh please stop lying
Please stop la la la la la la
La la la la la...
La la la la la...

yingyinNormal.en: I'm not your enemy! Plankton is your enemy!
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不是你们的敌人！痞老板才是！
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《The SpongeBob Movie: Sponge Out of Water》

yingyinNormal.en: The truth is we really don't understand our enemy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 事实上，我们完全不了解我们的敌人。

yingyinNormal.en: America is our enemy and must meet our demands.
yingyinNormal.zh: 美国是我们的敌人，必须满足我们的需求。

yingyinNormal.en: Steve. You are your own worst enemy. And this company's.
yingyinNormal.zh: 史蒂夫，你是你自己最坏的敌人，同时也是公司的

yingyinNormal.en: Operation Downfall isn't our end game. It's the enemy's.
yingyinNormal.zh: 其实这场战争，不是我们的收官之战，而是敌人的。

yingyinNormal.en: These people are not your enemy! We all have one enemy. And that's Snow.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这些人不是你的敌人，我们都只有一个敌人，就是斯诺。

yingyinNormal.en: You must learn to control it. Fear will be your enemy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你一定要学会掌控力量。恐惧会成为你的敌人。

yingyinNormal.en: Our survival demands total commitment to the destruction of the enemy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 要想生存下去就必须全面剿灭敌人。

yingyinNormal.en: And we are facing an enemy that will not change and will never surrender.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而我们的敌人将永不改变永不投降。

yingyinNormal.en: And we have to destroy him. But he is not our enemy. Not today.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们要摧毁他。但他不是我们的敌人。今天不是。

yingyinNormal.en: We will never forget what the enemy did. But we defeated them.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们不会遗忘敌人的所作所为，但我们打败了他们。

yingyinNormal.en: Above all, they mustn't fall into enemy hands. So Ajay survived as well.
yingyinNormal.zh: 绝对不能落到敌人的手里。阿杰也活下来了。

yingyinNormal.en: We have an ally? Ultron's got an enemy. That's not the same thing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们有个盟友吗？是奥创有个敌人，这两者可不一样。

yingyinNormal.en: When you killed that Alpha, you inadvertently entered the enemy's nervous system.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你杀掉阿尔法的时候，无意中进入了敌人的神经系统。

yingyinNormal.en: He says humans would only see you as the enemy. He wants me to roll you back.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他说人类只会将你视为敌人，他想让我对你进行回滚操作。

yingyinNormal.en: When the enemy first invaded, we were not ready. Millions of innocent lives were lost.
yingyinNormal.zh: 敌人第一次入侵时，我们毫无防备，数百万无辜的人丧命。

yingyinNormal.en: You needed time. Time to understand your enemy. To become stronger than them.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你当时需要时间，你需要时间来了解你的敌人，变得比他们更强大。

yingyinNormal.en: When the virus gets through, the cell recognizes its mistake. An enemy is inside!
yingyinNormal.zh: 当病毒在里面了以后，细胞认识到它犯的错误。敌人到里面来了！

yingyinNormal.en: We should simply ask the enemy not to invade on a Sabbath cause Private Doss here is a prayer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们应要求敌人别在安息日进攻因为列兵多斯在此祈祷。

yingyinNormal.en: You won't believe me when I tell you that Dr. Carter was right that the enemy can manipulate time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你不相信我告诉你的，卡特博士是正确的，敌人可以随意控制时间。

数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: a person who is actively opposed or hostile to someone or something

examination_example.sentence: Rats and other animals need to be highly attuned to social signals from others so they can identify friends to cooperate with and <highlight>enemies</highlight> to avoid.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 老鼠等动物需要对同类发出的社交信号高度敏感，这样它们才能分辨哪些是可以合作的朋友，哪些是应该避开的敌人。

examination_example.sentence: What political journalist would not want to know the makeup of the WhatsApp groups in which Theresa May's <highlight>enemies</highlight> are currently plotting?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 特蕾莎·梅的政敌正在其中进行密谋的那些WhatsApp聊天群，哪个政治记者会不想知道其成员构成？

examination_example.sentence: Charles ought to know that as English history shows, it is kings, not republicans, who are the monarchy's worst <highlight>enemies</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 查理应该知道，英国历史表明，国王才是君主制最大的敌人，而不是共和党人。

word_usage.usage:
enemy与定冠词连用在句中可以作集体名词。当它作主语指代一个集体时谓语动词用单数；当强调群体中所有成员时谓语动词用复数。如：
The enemy consists of 200 soldiers.
敌军有两百个士兵。
The enemy were forced to give in.
敌人被迫投降。

examination_example.sentence: Because of my daughter, I learned that I was the biggest <highlight>enemy</highlight> to my own happiness.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 因为我的女儿，我知道我是自己幸福的最大敌人。

examination_example.sentence: Some <highlight>enemies</highlight> decided to cheat them out of their property (财产) by making them quarrel about it.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一些敌人决定骗取他们的财产，让他们为之争吵。

examination_example.sentence: How do zebras protect themselves from their <highlight>enemies</highlight>?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 斑马是如何保护自己不受敌人伤害的？
